vstore.framework.context

Class ContextDescription

  • java.lang.Object
    • vstore.framework.context.ContextDescription
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SearchContextDescription

    public class ContextDescription
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents the description of a context. It contains location, nearby places, network connectivity, time, events. Not every type of context has to be available in every situation, so you should better check if it is null before using it.
    See Also:
